All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Geometry, GeometryCollection
public class BaseGeometryArray
extends BaseGeometry
implements GeometryCollection

Provides a simple array-based implementation of GeometryCollection. To use it, specify the desired array size in the constructor, then add each Geometry to the collection.
